DTSTART;TZID=America/Halifax:20260424T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Halifax:20260424T203000
DTSTAMP:20260330T230919
CREATED:20260212T142834Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260317T144339Z
UID:8189-1777053600-1777062600@hardtruth.com
SUMMARY:Cask & Still Social
DESCRIPTION:Be among the first to experience our Wheated Bourbon Mizunara Barrel Finish Reserve before the official release on May 9th. \nAt the Cask & Still Social\, immerse yourself in the world of exceptional whiskey\, delectable food\, and engaging conversation with whiskey experts for $60. Enjoy a laid-back\, welcoming atmosphere as you connect with fellow enthusiasts and savor the rich flavors of Sweet Mash Whiskeys with signature cocktails and a curated selection of samples. \nThis 2.5-hour event will feature whiskey tasting stations\, passed appetizers\, and the opportunity to deepen your knowledge of the Hard Truth brand through expert-led discussions. Meet our brand ambassadors and talented staff who\, will guide you through each tasting experience\, providing insights into the artistry behind each whiskey expression. \nWhether you’re a connoisseur or new to whiskey\, this event promises an unforgettable evening. Limited spots are available — secure your place today!
URL:https://hardtruth.com/event/cask-still-social-4/
CATEGORIES:Featured
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Hard Truth Distilling Co.
X-SOURCE-URL:https://hardtruth.com/events/ (Nashville, IN - 16 mi)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Halifax:20260509T080000
DTEND;TZID=America/Halifax:20260509T170000
DTSTAMP:20260330T230919
CREATED:20260105T185236Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260317T133555Z
UID:8143-1778313600-1778346000@hardtruth.com
SUMMARY:Hard Truth On The Rocks Opening Day!
DESCRIPTION:Join us Friday\, May 9\, for opening weekend of the Hard Truth Terrace and the debut of our Wheated Bourbon finished on Mizunara oak. \nWe’ll be celebrating this rare release with cocktails\, guided tastings\, and seasonal food offerings in the open air. \nStarting at noon\, the terrace will start welcoming guests for: \n\nSpecialty cocktails\, guided tastings\, and bottle sales of Hard Truth Wheated Bourbon finished on Mizunara oak\nSeasonal bites from the terrace bar\nOutdoor seating\nEvening live music\n\nWith warmer weather\, fresh flavors\, and a standout release\, terrace season starts here. \n 
URL:https://hardtruth.com/event/hard-truth-on-the-rocks-opening-day-2/
CATEGORIES:Featured
END:VEVENT
